<div>
GCrawler (1) searchs Google Code and discovers all Grails projects, (2) reads Subversion repository to figure out metadata, and (3) automatically add them to Hudson and builds them.
This plugin requires <a href="http://wiki.hudson-ci.org/display/HUDSON/Google+Code+Plugin">Google Code Plugin</a> and <a href="http://wiki.hudson-ci.org/display/HUDSON/Grails+Plugin">Grails Plugin</a>.
</div>